ZM  MARIO   ASHKINS

--------

This map has 3 cade rooms plus the big one having two possible zombie entrances

The ? blocks in the 2nd cade room are breakable

There is a container that adds 2 survival chances (In the container and On the container)

the 2nd cade room has a ceiling that can be accesed with a ladder. and a couch to prevent the

zombies to enter.

Have fun !.
